(jdoN mnu`K pRBU dy dr qy if`gdw hY, qW mwieAw dw twkrw krn leI aus dy AMdr Awqmk) bl pYdw ho jWdw hY (mwieAw dy moh dy) bMDn tu`t jWdy hn (moh dw twkrw krn leI) hryk hIlw sPl ho skdw hY[
so, hy nwnk AwKdw hY- (hy pRBU!) sB kuJ qyry h`Q ivc hY (qyrI pYdw kIqI mwieAw BI qyry hI ADIn hY, ies qoN bcx leI) qUM hI mddgwr ho skdw hYN ]54]
